title: Lavish Amenities, Walk to Shopping & Dining, Heat is Paid
posting_body: ['Contact info:', 'Mike Miller | The Apartment Resource |', 'show contact info', '2BR/1BA Apartment - Maple Grove', 'Hwy 94, Maple Grove, MN 55311', '$1,900/mo', 'KEY FEATURES', 'Sq Footage:', '1049 sqft.', 'Bedrooms:', '1 Plus Den', 'Bathroom:', '1 Full Bath', 'Parking:', '2 | 1 Heated Garage Parking Spot', 'Lease Duration:', '1 Year', 'Deposit:', '$350', 'Pets Policy:', 'Dogs and Cats Ok', 'Laundry:', 'In Unit', 'Property Type:', 'Apartment', 'DESCRIPTION', 'Our community amenities include a fitness center, entertainment room with kitchen, screened porch, log balconies, computer room with wi-fi, and underground heated garage parking with car wash bay.', 'Heat is included in rent.', 'A convenient Maple Grove location near the Shops at Arbor Lakes, many walking and jogging trails, and several lakes including Rice Lake and Weaver Lake.', 'You will have convenient highway access to 94 and 101 for easy access to Boston Scientificm, downtown Minneapolis and all around the metro.', 'A place where the beauty of the north meets the convenience of the big city, where you can connect with friends or with nature.', "Shop til' you drop at nearby stores or dine to your hearts delight.", 'Curl up with a good book and make memories in our beautiful north woods community rooms!', 'Prices and availability are subject to change.', ' Photos may not represent exact unit.', 'Call Mike to tour.', 'show contact info', 'RENTAL FEATURES', 'Dining room', 'Walk-in closet', 'Family room', 'Stove / Oven', 'Refrigerator', 'Dishwasher', 'Microwave', 'Balcony, Deck, or Patio', 'Lake', 'Air conditioning', 'Cable-ready', 'High-speed internet', 'Tile floor', 'Fireplace', 'High / Vaulted ceiling', 'COMMUNITY FEATURES', 'Fitness center', 'Clubhouse', 'Playground', 'Business center', 'Guest parking', 'LEASE TERMS', '12 Months', 'Contact info:', 'Mike Miller', 'The Apartment Resource', 'show contact info', 'Equal Housing Opportunity']
